122static void callExitSoon(IPC::Connection*)
123{
124 // If the connection has been closed and we haven't responded in the main thread for 10 seconds
125 // the process will exit forcibly.
126 auto watchdogDelay = 10_s;
127
128 WorkQueue::create("com.apple.WebKit.NetworkProcess.WatchDogQueue")->dispatchAfter(watchdogDelay, [] {
129 // We use _exit here since the watchdog callback is called from another thread and we don't want
130 // global destructors or atexit handlers to be called from this thread while the main thread is busy
131 // doing its thing.
132 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(IPC, "Exiting process early due to unacknowledged closed-connection");
133#if OS(WINDOWS)
134 // Calling _exit in non-main threads may cause a deadlock in WTF::Thread::ThreadHolder::~ThreadHolder.
135 TerminateProcess(GetCurrentProcess(), EXIT_FAILURE);
136#else
137 _exit(EXIT_FAILURE);
138#endif
139 });
140}
141
142static inline MessagePortChannelRegistry createMessagePortChannelRegistry(NetworkProcess& networkProcess)
143{
144 return MessagePortChannelRegistry { [&networkProcess](auto& messagePortIdentifier, auto processIdentifier, auto&& completionHandler) {
145 auto* connection = networkProcess.webProcessConnection(processIdentifier);
146 if (!connection) {
147 completionHandler(MessagePortChannelProvider::HasActivity::No);
148 return;
149 }
150
151 connection->checkProcessLocalPortForActivity(messagePortIdentifier, WTFMove(completionHandler));
152 } };
153}
154
155NetworkProcess::NetworkProcess(AuxiliaryProcessInitializationParameters&& parameters)
156 : m_downloadManager(*this)
157 , m_storageManagerSet(StorageManagerSet::create())
158#if ENABLE(CONTENT_EXTENSIONS)
159 , m_networkContentRuleListManager(*this)
160#endif
161#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
162 , m_webSQLiteDatabaseTracker([this](bool isHoldingLockedFiles) { setIsHoldingLockedFiles(isHoldingLockedFiles); })
163#endif
164 , m_messagePortChannelRegistry(createMessagePortChannelRegistry(*this))
165{
166 NetworkProcessPlatformStrategies::initialize();
167
168 addSupplement<AuthenticationManager>();
169 addSupplement<WebCookieManager>();
170#if ENABLE(LEGACY_CUSTOM_PROTOCOL_MANAGER)
171 addSupplement<LegacyCustomProtocolManager>();
172#endif
173#if HAVE(LSDATABASECONTEXT)
174 addSupplement<LaunchServicesDatabaseObserver>();
175#endif
176#if PLATFORM(COCOA) && ENABLE(LEGACY_CUSTOM_PROTOCOL_MANAGER)
177 LegacyCustomProtocolManager::networkProcessCreated(*this);
178#endif
179
180 NetworkStateNotifier::singleton().addListener([weakThis = makeWeakPtr(*this)](bool isOnLine) {
181 if (!weakThis)
182 return;
183 for (auto& webProcessConnection : weakThis->m_webProcessConnections.values())
184 webProcessConnection->setOnLineState(isOnLine);
185 });
186
187 initialize(WTFMove(parameters));
188}
189
190NetworkProcess::~NetworkProcess()
191{
192 for (auto& callbacks : m_cacheStorageParametersCallbacks.values()) {
193 for (auto& callback : callbacks)
194 callback(String { });
195 }
196}

208void NetworkProcess::removeNetworkConnectionToWebProcess(NetworkConnectionToWebProcess& connection)
209{
210 ASSERT(m_webProcessConnections.contains(connection.webProcessIdentifier()));
211 m_webProcessConnections.remove(connection.webProcessIdentifier());
212}
213
214bool NetworkProcess::shouldTerminate()
215{
216 // Network process keeps session cookies and credentials, so it should never terminate (as long as UI process connection is alive).
217 return false;
218}
219
220void NetworkProcess::didReceiveMessage(IPC::Connection& connection, IPC::Decoder& decoder)
221{
222 ASSERT(parentProcessConnection() == &connection);
223 if (parentProcessConnection() != &connection) {
224 WTFLogAlways("Ignored message '%s' because it did not come from the UIProcess (destination=%" PRIu64 ")", description(decoder.messageName()), decoder.destinationID());
225 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
226 return;
227 }
228
229 if (messageReceiverMap().dispatchMessage(connection, decoder))
230 return;
231
232 if (decoder.messageReceiverName() == Messages::AuxiliaryProcess::messageReceiverName()) {
233 AuxiliaryProcess::didReceiveMessage(connection, decoder);
234 return;
235 }
236
237#if ENABLE(CONTENT_EXTENSIONS)
238 if (decoder.messageReceiverName() == Messages::NetworkContentRuleListManager::messageReceiverName()) {
239 m_networkContentRuleListManager.didReceiveMessage(connection, decoder);
240 return;
241 }
242#endif
243
244 didReceiveNetworkProcessMessage(connection, decoder);
245}
246
247bool NetworkProcess::didReceiveSyncMessage(IPC::Connection& connection, IPC::Decoder& decoder, UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>& replyEncoder)
248{
249 ASSERT(parentProcessConnection() == &connection);
250 if (parentProcessConnection() != &connection) {
251 WTFLogAlways("Ignored message '%s' because it did not come from the UIProcess (destination=%" PRIu64 ")", description(decoder.messageName()), decoder.destinationID());
252 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
253 return false;
254 }
255
256 if (messageReceiverMap().dispatchSyncMessage(connection, decoder, replyEncoder))
257 return true;
258
259 return didReceiveSyncNetworkProcessMessage(connection, decoder, replyEncoder);
260}
261
262void NetworkProcess::didClose(IPC::Connection&)
263{
264 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
265
266 auto callbackAggregator = CallbackAggregator::create([this] {
267 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
268 stopRunLoop();
269 });
270
271 // Make sure we flush all cookies to disk before exiting.
272 forEachNetworkSession([&] (auto& networkSession) {
273 platformFlushCookies(networkSession.sessionID(), [callbackAggregator] { });
274 });
275
276 // Make sure reference to NetworkProcess in spaceRequester is removed.
277 auto servers = std::exchange(m_webIDBServers, { });
278 for (auto& server : servers.values())
279 server->close([callbackAggregator] { });
280}

301
302void NetworkProcess::lowMemoryHandler(Critical critical)
303{
304 if (m_suppressMemoryPressureHandler)
305 return;
306
307 WTF::releaseFastMallocFreeMemory();
308
309 forEachNetworkSession([](auto& networkSession) {
310 networkSession.clearPrefetchCache();
311 });
312
313 m_storageManagerSet->handleLowMemoryWarning();
314
315#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
316 for (auto& swServer : m_swServers.values())
317 swServer->handleLowMemoryWarning();
318#endif
319}
320
321void NetworkProcess::initializeNetworkProcess(NetworkProcessCreationParameters&& parameters)
322{
323#if HAVE(SEC_KEY_PROXY)
324 WTF::setProcessPrivileges({ ProcessPrivilege::CanAccessRawCookies });
325#else
326 WTF::setProcessPrivileges({ ProcessPrivilege::CanAccessRawCookies, ProcessPrivilege::CanAccessCredentials });
327#endif
328 WebCore::NetworkStorageSession::permitProcessToUseCookieAPI(true);
329 platformInitializeNetworkProcess(parameters);
330
331 WTF::Thread::setCurrentThreadIsUserInitiated();
332 AtomString::init();
333
334 m_suppressMemoryPressureHandler = parameters.shouldSuppressMemoryPressureHandler;
335 if (!m_suppressMemoryPressureHandler) {
336 auto& memoryPressureHandler = MemoryPressureHandler::singleton();
337 memoryPressureHandler.setLowMemoryHandler([this] (Critical critical, Synchronous) {
338 lowMemoryHandler(critical);
339 });
340 memoryPressureHandler.install();
341 }
342
343 setCacheModel(parameters.cacheModel);
344
345 setPrivateClickMeasurementEnabled(parameters.enablePrivateClickMeasurement);
346 setPrivateClickMeasurementDebugMode(parameters.enablePrivateClickMeasurementDebugMode);
347
348 for (auto& supplement : m_supplements.values())
349 supplement->initialize(parameters);
350
351 for (auto& scheme : parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsSecure)
352 registerURLSchemeAsSecure(scheme);
353
354 for (auto& scheme : parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsBypassingContentSecurityPolicy)
355 registerURLSchemeAsBypassingContentSecurityPolicy(scheme);
356
357 for (auto& scheme : parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsLocal)
358 registerURLSchemeAsLocal(scheme);
359
360 for (auto& scheme : parameters.urlSchemesRegisteredAsNoAccess)
361 registerURLSchemeAsNoAccess(scheme);
362
363 for (auto&& websiteDataStoreParameters : WTFMove(parameters.websiteDataStoreParameters))
364 addWebsiteDataStore(WTFMove(websiteDataStoreParameters));
365
366 RELEASE_LOG(Process, "%p - NetworkProcess::initializeNetworkProcess: Presenting processPID=%d", this, WebCore::presentingApplicationPID());
367}
368
369void NetworkProcess::initializeConnection(IPC::Connection* connection)
370{
371 AuxiliaryProcess::initializeConnection(connection);
372
373 // We give a chance for didClose() to get called on the main thread but forcefully call _exit() after a delay
374 // in case the main thread is unresponsive or didClose() takes too long.
375 connection->setDidCloseOnConnectionWorkQueueCallback(callExitSoon);
376
377 for (auto& supplement : m_supplements.values())
378 supplement->initializeConnection(connection);
379}
380
381void NetworkProcess::createNetworkConnectionToWebProcess(ProcessIdentifier identifier, PAL::SessionID sessionID, CompletionHandler<void(std::optional<IPC::Attachment>&&, HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy)>&& completionHandler)
382{
383 auto ipcConnection = createIPCConnectionPair();
384 if (!ipcConnection) {
385 completionHandler({ }, HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy::Never);
386 return;
387 }
388
389 auto newConnection = NetworkConnectionToWebProcess::create(*this, identifier, sessionID, ipcConnection->first);
390 auto& connection = newConnection.get();
391
392 ASSERT(!m_webProcessConnections.contains(identifier));
393 m_webProcessConnections.add(identifier, WTFMove(newConnection));
394
395 auto* storage = storageSession(sessionID);
396 completionHandler(WTFMove(ipcConnection->second), storage ? storage->cookieAcceptPolicy() : HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy::Never);
397
398 connection.setOnLineState(NetworkStateNotifier::singleton().onLine());
399
400 m_storageManagerSet->addConnection(connection.connection());
401}
402
403void NetworkProcess::clearCachedCredentials(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
404{
405 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
406 if (auto* storageSession = networkSession->networkStorageSession())
407 storageSession->credentialStorage().clearCredentials();
408 networkSession->clearCredentials();
409 }
410}
411
412void NetworkProcess::addWebsiteDataStore(WebsiteDataStoreParameters&& parameters)
413{
414 auto sessionID = parameters.networkSessionParameters.sessionID;
415
416 addSessionStorageQuotaManager(sessionID, parameters.perOriginStorageQuota, parameters.perThirdPartyOriginStorageQuota, parameters.cacheStorageDirectory, parameters.cacheStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
417
418 addIndexedDatabaseSession(sessionID, parameters.indexedDatabaseDirectory, parameters.indexedDatabaseDirectoryExtensionHandle);
419
420#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
421 addServiceWorkerSession(sessionID, parameters.serviceWorkerProcessTerminationDelayEnabled, WTFMove(parameters.serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory), parameters.serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectoryExtensionHandle);
422#endif
423
424 m_storageManagerSet->add(sessionID, parameters.localStorageDirectory, parameters.localStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
425
426 RemoteNetworkingContext::ensureWebsiteDataStoreSession(*this, WTFMove(parameters));
427}
428
429void NetworkProcess::addSessionStorageQuotaManager(PAL::SessionID sessionID, uint64_t defaultQuota, uint64_t defaultThirdPartyQuota, const String& cacheRootPath, SandboxExtension::Handle& cacheRootPathHandle)
430{
431 Locker locker { m_sessionStorageQuotaManagersLock };
432 auto isNewEntry = m_sessionStorageQuotaManagers.ensure(sessionID, [defaultQuota, defaultThirdPartyQuota, &cacheRootPath] {
433 return makeUnique<SessionStorageQuotaManager>(cacheRootPath, defaultQuota, defaultThirdPartyQuota);
434 }).isNewEntry;
435 if (isNewEntry)
436 SandboxExtension::consumePermanently(cacheRootPathHandle);
437 else
438 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
439}
440
441void NetworkProcess::removeSessionStorageQuotaManager(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
442{
443 Locker locker { m_sessionStorageQuotaManagersLock };
444 ASSERT(m_sessionStorageQuotaManagers.contains(sessionID));
445 m_sessionStorageQuotaManagers.remove(sessionID);
446}

450 for (auto& session : m_networkSessions.values())
451 functor(*session);
452}
453
454std::unique_ptr<WebCore::NetworkStorageSession> NetworkProcess::newTestingSession(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
455{
456#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
457 // Session name should be short enough for shared memory region name to be under the limit, otherwise sandbox rules won't work (see <rdar://problem/13642852>).
458 auto session = WebCore::createPrivateStorageSession(makeString("WebKit Test-", getCurrentProcessID()).createCFString().get());
459 RetainPtr<CFHTTPCookieStorageRef> cookieStorage;
460 if (WebCore::NetworkStorageSession::processMayUseCookieAPI()) {
461 ASSERT(hasProcessPrivilege(ProcessPrivilege::CanAccessRawCookies));
462 if (session)
463 cookieStorage = adoptCF(_CFURLStorageSessionCopyCookieStorage(kCFAllocatorDefault, session.get()));
464 }
465 return makeUnique<WebCore::NetworkStorageSession>(sessionID, WTFMove(session), WTFMove(cookieStorage));
466#elif USE(CURL) || USE(SOUP)
467 return makeUnique<WebCore::NetworkStorageSession>(sessionID);
468#endif
469}
470
471#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
472void NetworkProcess::ensureSession(PAL::SessionID sessionID, bool shouldUseTestingNetworkSession, const String& identifierBase, RetainPtr<CFHTTPCookieStorageRef>&& cookieStorage)
473#else
474void NetworkProcess::ensureSession(PAL::SessionID sessionID, bool shouldUseTestingNetworkSession, const String& identifierBase)
475#endif
476{
477 auto addResult = m_networkStorageSessions.add(sessionID, nullptr);
478 if (!addResult.isNewEntry)
479 return;
480
481 if (shouldUseTestingNetworkSession) {
482 addResult.iterator->value = newTestingSession(sessionID);
483 return;
484 }
485
486#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
487 RetainPtr<CFURLStorageSessionRef> storageSession;
488 RetainPtr<CFStringRef> cfIdentifier = makeString(identifierBase, ".PrivateBrowsing.", createCanonicalUUIDString()).createCFString();
489 if (sessionID.isEphemeral())
490 storageSession = createPrivateStorageSession(cfIdentifier.get());
491 else if (sessionID != PAL::SessionID::defaultSessionID())
492 storageSession = WebCore::NetworkStorageSession::createCFStorageSessionForIdentifier(cfIdentifier.get());
493
494 if (NetworkStorageSession::processMayUseCookieAPI()) {
495 ASSERT(hasProcessPrivilege(ProcessPrivilege::CanAccessRawCookies));
496 if (!cookieStorage && storageSession)
497 cookieStorage = adoptCF(_CFURLStorageSessionCopyCookieStorage(kCFAllocatorDefault, storageSession.get()));
498 }
499
500 addResult.iterator->value = makeUnique<NetworkStorageSession>(sessionID, WTFMove(storageSession), WTFMove(cookieStorage));
501#elif USE(CURL) || USE(SOUP)
502 addResult.iterator->value = makeUnique<NetworkStorageSession>(sessionID);
503#endif
504}

529void NetworkProcess::setSession(PAL::SessionID sessionID, std::unique_ptr<NetworkSession>&& session)
530{
531 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
532 m_networkSessions.set(sessionID, WTFMove(session));
533}
534
535void NetworkProcess::destroySession(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
536{
537 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
538#if !USE(SOUP) && !USE(CURL)
539 // cURL and Soup based ports destroy the default session right before the process exits to avoid leaking
540 // network resources like the cookies database.
541 ASSERT(sessionID != PAL::SessionID::defaultSessionID());
542#endif
543
544 if (auto session = m_networkSessions.take(sessionID))
545 session->invalidateAndCancel();
546 m_networkStorageSessions.remove(sessionID);
547 m_sessionsControlledByAutomation.remove(sessionID);
548 CacheStorage::Engine::destroyEngine(*this, sessionID);
549
550#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
551 m_swServers.remove(sessionID);
552 m_serviceWorkerInfo.remove(sessionID);
553#endif
554
555 m_storageManagerSet->remove(sessionID);
556 if (auto server = m_webIDBServers.take(sessionID))
557 server->close();
558}

560#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
561void NetworkProcess::dumpResourceLoadStatistics(PAL::SessionID sessionID, CompletionHandler<void(String)>&& completionHandler)
562{
563 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
564 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = networkSession->resourceLoadStatistics())
565 resourceLoadStatistics->dumpResourceLoadStatistics(WTFMove(completionHandler));
566 else
567 completionHandler({ });
568 } else {
569 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
570 completionHandler({ });
571 }
572}

581void NetworkProcess::isGrandfathered(PAL::SessionID sessionID, const RegistrableDomain& domain, CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
582{
583 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
584 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = networkSession->resourceLoadStatistics())
585 resourceLoadStatistics->isGrandfathered(domain, WTFMove(completionHandler));
586 else
587 completionHandler(false);
588 } else {
589 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
590 completionHandler(false);
591 }
592}

1201
1202void NetworkProcess::didCommitCrossSiteLoadWithDataTransfer(PAL::SessionID sessionID, const RegistrableDomain& fromDomain, const RegistrableDomain& toDomain, OptionSet<WebCore::CrossSiteNavigationDataTransfer::Flag> navigationDataTransfer, WebPageProxyIdentifier webPageProxyID, WebCore::PageIdentifier webPageID)
1203{
1204 ASSERT(!navigationDataTransfer.isEmpty());
1205
1206 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID)) {
1207 if (!networkStorageSession->shouldBlockThirdPartyCookies(fromDomain))
1208 return;
1209
1210 if (navigationDataTransfer.contains(CrossSiteNavigationDataTransfer::Flag::DestinationLinkDecoration))
1211 networkStorageSession->didCommitCrossSiteLoadWithDataTransferFromPrevalentResource(toDomain, webPageID);
1212
1213 if (navigationDataTransfer.contains(CrossSiteNavigationDataTransfer::Flag::ReferrerLinkDecoration))
1214 parentProcessConnection()->send(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::DidCommitCrossSiteLoadWithDataTransferFromPrevalentResource(webPageProxyID), 0);
1215 } else
1216 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1217
1218 if (navigationDataTransfer.contains(CrossSiteNavigationDataTransfer::Flag::DestinationLinkDecoration)) {
1219 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1220 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = networkSession->resourceLoadStatistics())
1221 resourceLoadStatistics->logCrossSiteLoadWithLinkDecoration(fromDomain, toDomain, [] { });
1222 } else
1223 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1224 }
1225}
1226
1227void NetworkProcess::setCrossSiteLoadWithLinkDecorationForTesting(PAL::SessionID sessionID, const RegistrableDomain& fromDomain, const RegistrableDomain& toDomain, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1228{
1229 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1230 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = networkSession->resourceLoadStatistics())
1231 resourceLoadStatistics->logCrossSiteLoadWithLinkDecoration(fromDomain, toDomain, WTFMove(completionHandler));

1233 completionHandler();
1234 } else {
1235 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1236 completionHandler();
1237 }
1238}

1345void NetworkProcess::setPrivateClickMeasurementDebugMode(bool enabled)
1346{
1347 if (m_privateClickMeasurementDebugModeEnabled == enabled)
1348 return;
1349
1350 m_privateClickMeasurementDebugModeEnabled = enabled;
1351
1352 String message = enabled ? "[Private Click Measurement] Turned Debug Mode on."_s : "[Private Click Measurement] Turned Debug Mode off."_s;
1353 for (auto& networkConnectionToWebProcess : m_webProcessConnections.values()) {
1354 if (networkConnectionToWebProcess->sessionID().isEphemeral())
1355 continue;
1356 networkConnectionToWebProcess->broadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::PrivateClickMeasurement, MessageLevel::Info, message);

1364
1365void NetworkProcess::preconnectTo(PAL::SessionID sessionID, WebPageProxyIdentifier webPageProxyID, WebCore::PageIdentifier webPageID, const URL& url, const String& userAgent, WebCore::StoredCredentialsPolicy storedCredentialsPolicy, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, LastNavigationWasAppBound lastNavigationWasAppBound)
1366{
1367 LOG(Network, "(NetworkProcess) Preconnecting to URL %s (storedCredentialsPolicy %i)", url.string().utf8().data(), (int)storedCredentialsPolicy);
1368
1369#if ENABLE(SERVER_PRECONNECT)
1370#if ENABLE(LEGACY_CUSTOM_PROTOCOL_MANAGER)
1371 if (supplement<LegacyCustomProtocolManager>()->supportsScheme(url.protocol().toString()))
1372 return;
1373#endif
1374
1375 auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID);
1376 if (!networkSession)
1377 return;
1378
1379 NetworkLoadParameters parameters;
1380 parameters.request = ResourceRequest { url };
1381 parameters.request.setIsAppBound(lastNavigationWasAppBound == LastNavigationWasAppBound::Yes);
1382 parameters.request.setFirstPartyForCookies(url);
1383 parameters.webPageProxyID = webPageProxyID;
1384 parameters.webPageID = webPageID;
1385 parameters.isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain = isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain;
1386 if (!userAgent.isEmpty()) {
1387 // FIXME: we add user-agent to the preconnect request because otherwise the preconnect
1388 // gets thrown away by CFNetwork when using an HTTPS proxy (<rdar://problem/59434166>).
1389 parameters.request.setHTTPUserAgent(userAgent);
1390 }
1391 parameters.storedCredentialsPolicy = storedCredentialsPolicy;
1392 parameters.shouldPreconnectOnly = PreconnectOnly::Yes;
1393
1394 (new PreconnectTask(*networkSession, WTFMove(parameters), [](const WebCore::ResourceError&) { }))->start();
1395#else
1396 UNUSED_PARAM(url);
1397 UNUSED_PARAM(userAgent);
1398 UNUSED_PARAM(storedCredentialsPolicy);
1399#endif
1400}

1414
1415static void fetchDiskCacheEntries(NetworkCache::Cache* cache, PAL::SessionID sessionID, OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebsiteData::Entry>)>&& completionHandler)
1416{
1417 if (!cache) {
1418 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] () mutable {
1419 completionHandler({ });
1420 });
1421 return;
1422 }
1423
1424 HashMap<SecurityOriginData, uint64_t> originsAndSizes;
1425 cache->traverse([fetchOptions, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), originsAndSizes = WTFMove(originsAndSizes)](auto* traversalEntry) mutable {
1426 if (!traversalEntry) {
1427 Vector<WebsiteData::Entry> entries;
1428
1429 for (auto& originAndSize : originsAndSizes)
1430 entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { originAndSize.key, WebsiteDataType::DiskCache, originAndSize.value });
1431
1432 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), entries = WTFMove(entries)] () mutable {
1433 completionHandler(entries);
1434 });
1435
1436 return;
1437 }
1438
1439 auto url = traversalEntry->entry.response().url();
1440 auto result = originsAndSizes.add({url.protocol().toString(), url.host().toString(), url.port()}, 0);
1441
1442 if (fetchOptions.contains(WebsiteDataFetchOption::ComputeSizes))
1443 result.iterator->value += traversalEntry->entry.sourceStorageRecord().header.size() + traversalEntry->recordInfo.bodySize;
1444 });
1445}
1446
1447void NetworkProcess::fetchWebsiteData(PAL::SessionID sessionID, OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> websiteDataTypes, OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, CompletionHandler<void(WebsiteData&&)>&& completionHandler)
1448{
1449 struct CallbackAggregator final : public ThreadSafeRefCounted<CallbackAggregator> {
1450 explicit CallbackAggregator(CompletionHandler<void(WebsiteData&&)>&& completionHandler)
1451 : m_completionHandler(WTFMove(completionHandler))
1452 {
1453 }
1454
1455 ~CallbackAggregator()
1456 {
1457 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(m_completionHandler), websiteData = WTFMove(m_websiteData)] () mutable {
1458 completionHandler(WTFMove(websiteData));
1459 });
1460 }
1461
1462 CompletionHandler<void(WebsiteData&&)> m_completionHandler;
1463 WebsiteData m_websiteData;
1464 };
1465
1466 auto callbackAggregator = adoptRef(*new CallbackAggregator(WTFMove(completionHandler)));
1467
1468 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies)) {
1469 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID))
1470 networkStorageSession->getHostnamesWithCookies(callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.hostNamesWithCookies);
1471 }
1472
1473 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Credentials)) {
1474 if (storageSession(sessionID)) {
1475 auto securityOrigins = storageSession(sessionID)->credentialStorage().originsWithCredentials();
1476 for (auto& securityOrigin : securityOrigins)
1477 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ securityOrigin, WebsiteDataType::Credentials, 0 });
1478 }
1479 auto securityOrigins = WebCore::CredentialStorage::originsWithSessionCredentials();
1480 for (auto& securityOrigin : securityOrigins)
1481 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ securityOrigin, WebsiteDataType::Credentials, 0 });
1482 }
1483
1484 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache)) {
1485 CacheStorage::Engine::fetchEntries(*this, sessionID, fetchOptions.contains(WebsiteDataFetchOption::ComputeSizes), [callbackAggregator](auto entries) mutable {
1486 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.appendVector(entries);
1487 });
1488 }
1489
1490 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::SessionStorage) && m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID)) {
1491 m_storageManagerSet->getSessionStorageOrigins(sessionID, [callbackAggregator](auto&& origins) {
1492 while (!origins.isEmpty())
1493 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origins.takeAny(), WebsiteDataType::SessionStorage, 0 });
1494 });
1495 }
1496
1497 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage) && m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID)) {
1498 m_storageManagerSet->getLocalStorageOrigins(sessionID, [callbackAggregator](auto&& origins) {
1499 while (!origins.isEmpty())
1500 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origins.takeAny(), WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage, 0 });
1501 });
1502 }
1503
1504#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || USE(SOUP)
1505 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::HSTSCache))
1506 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.hostNamesWithHSTSCache = hostNamesWithHSTSCache(sessionID);
1507#endif
1508
1509 auto path = m_idbDatabasePaths.get(sessionID);
1510 if (!path.isEmpty() && websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases)) {
1511 webIDBServer(sessionID).getOrigins([callbackAggregator](auto&& origins) {
1512 while (!origins.isEmpty())
1513 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ origins.takeAny(), WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases, 0 });
1514 });
1515 }
1516
1517#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
1518 path = m_serviceWorkerInfo.get(sessionID).databasePath;
1519 if (!path.isEmpty() && websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations)) {
1520 swServerForSession(sessionID).getOriginsWithRegistrations([callbackAggregator](const HashSet<SecurityOriginData>& securityOrigins) mutable {
1521 for (auto& origin : securityOrigins)
1522 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ origin, WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations, 0 });
1523 });
1524 }
1525#endif
1526 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache)) {
1527 forEachNetworkSession([sessionID, fetchOptions, &callbackAggregator](auto& session) {
1528 fetchDiskCacheEntries(session.cache(), sessionID, fetchOptions, [callbackAggregator](auto entries) mutable {
1529 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.appendVector(entries);
1530 });
1531 });
1532 }
1533
1534#if HAVE(CFNETWORK_ALTERNATIVE_SERVICE)
1535 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::AlternativeServices)) {
1536 if (auto* session = networkSession(sessionID)) {
1537 for (auto& origin : session->hostNamesWithAlternativeServices())
1538 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ origin, WebsiteDataType::AlternativeServices, 0 });
1539 }
1540 }
1541#endif
1542
1543#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1544 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ResourceLoadStatistics)) {
1545 if (auto* session = networkSession(sessionID)) {
1546 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = session->resourceLoadStatistics()) {
1547 resourceLoadStatistics->registrableDomains([callbackAggregator](auto&& domains) mutable {
1548 while (!domains.isEmpty())
1549 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.registrableDomainsWithResourceLoadStatistics.add(domains.takeLast());
1550 });
1551 }
1552 }
1553 }
1554#endif
1555}
1556
1557void NetworkProcess::deleteWebsiteData(PAL::SessionID sessionID, OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> websiteDataTypes, WallTime modifiedSince, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1558{
1559#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || USE(SOUP)
1560 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::HSTSCache))
1561 clearHSTSCache(sessionID, modifiedSince);
1562#endif
1563
1564 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies)) {
1565 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID))
1566 networkStorageSession->deleteAllCookiesModifiedSince(modifiedSince);
1567 }
1568
1569 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Credentials)) {
1570 if (auto* session = storageSession(sessionID))
1571 session->credentialStorage().clearCredentials();
1572 WebCore::CredentialStorage::clearSessionCredentials();
1573 }
1574
1575 auto clearTasksHandler = WTF::CallbackAggregator::create(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1576
1577 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache))
1578 CacheStorage::Engine::clearAllCaches(*this, sessionID, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1579
1580 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::SessionStorage) && m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
1581 m_storageManagerSet->deleteSessionStorage(sessionID, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1582
1583 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage) && m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
1584 m_storageManagerSet->deleteLocalStorageModifiedSince(sessionID, modifiedSince, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1585
1586 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases) && !sessionID.isEphemeral())
1587 webIDBServer(sessionID).closeAndDeleteDatabasesModifiedSince(modifiedSince, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1588
1589#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
1590 bool clearServiceWorkers = websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache) || websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations);
1591 if (clearServiceWorkers && !sessionID.isEphemeral())
1592 swServerForSession(sessionID).clearAll([clearTasksHandler] { });
1593#endif
1594
1595#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1596 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ResourceLoadStatistics)) {
1597 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1598 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = networkSession->resourceLoadStatistics()) {
1599 auto deletedTypesRaw = websiteDataTypes.toRaw();
1600 auto monitoredTypesRaw = WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::monitoredDataTypes().toRaw();
1601
1602 // If we are deleting all of the data types that the resource load statistics store monitors
1603 // we do not need to re-grandfather old data.
1604 auto shouldGrandfather = ((monitoredTypesRaw & deletedTypesRaw) == monitoredTypesRaw) ? ShouldGrandfatherStatistics::No : ShouldGrandfatherStatistics::Yes;
1605
1606 resourceLoadStatistics->scheduleClearInMemoryAndPersistent(modifiedSince, shouldGrandfather, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1607 }
1608 }
1609 }
1610#endif
1611
1612 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID))
1613 networkSession->removeNetworkWebsiteData(modifiedSince, std::nullopt, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1614
1615 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache) && !sessionID.isEphemeral())
1616 clearDiskCache(modifiedSince, [clearTasksHandler = WTFMove(clearTasksHandler)] { });
1617
1618 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::PrivateClickMeasurements)) {
1619 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID))
1620 networkSession->clearPrivateClickMeasurement();
1621 }
1622
1623#if HAVE(CFNETWORK_ALTERNATIVE_SERVICE)
1624 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::AlternativeServices)) {
1625 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID))
1626 networkSession->clearAlternativeServices(modifiedSince);
1627 }
1628#endif
1629}
1630
1631static void clearDiskCacheEntries(NetworkCache::Cache* cache, const Vector<SecurityOriginData>& origins, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1632{
1633 if (!cache) {
1634 RunLoop::main().dispatch(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1635 return;
1636 }
1637
1638 HashSet<RefPtr<SecurityOrigin>> originsToDelete;
1639 for (auto& origin : origins)
1640 originsToDelete.add(origin.securityOrigin());
1641
1642 Vector<NetworkCache::Key> cacheKeysToDelete;
1643 cache->traverse([cache, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), originsToDelete = WTFMove(originsToDelete), cacheKeysToDelete = WTFMove(cacheKeysToDelete)](auto* traversalEntry) mutable {
1644 if (traversalEntry) {
1645 if (originsToDelete.contains(SecurityOrigin::create(traversalEntry->entry.response().url())))
1646 cacheKeysToDelete.append(traversalEntry->entry.key());
1647 return;
1648 }
1649
1650 cache->remove(cacheKeysToDelete, WTFMove(completionHandler));
1651 return;
1652 });
1653}
1654
1655void NetworkProcess::deleteWebsiteDataForOrigins(PAL::SessionID sessionID, OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> websiteDataTypes, const Vector<SecurityOriginData>& originDatas, const Vector<String>& cookieHostNames, const Vector<String>& HSTSCacheHostNames, const Vector<RegistrableDomain>& registrableDomains, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1656{
1657 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies)) {
1658 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID))
1659 networkStorageSession->deleteCookiesForHostnames(cookieHostNames);
1660 }
1661
1662#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || USE(SOUP)
1663 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::HSTSCache))
1664 deleteHSTSCacheForHostNames(sessionID, HSTSCacheHostNames);
1665#endif
1666
1667#if HAVE(CFNETWORK_ALTERNATIVE_SERVICE)
1668 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::AlternativeServices)) {
1669 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1670 Vector<String> hosts;
1671 hosts.reserveInitialCapacity(originDatas.size());
1672 for (auto& origin : originDatas)
1673 hosts.uncheckedAppend(origin.host);
1674 networkSession->deleteAlternativeServicesForHostNames(hosts);
1675 }
1676 }
1677#endif
1678
1679 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::PrivateClickMeasurements)) {
1680 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1681 for (auto& originData : originDatas)
1682 networkSession->clearPrivateClickMeasurementForRegistrableDomain(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(originData.host));
1683 }
1684 }
1685
1686 auto clearTasksHandler = WTF::CallbackAggregator::create(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1687
1688 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache)) {
1689 for (auto& originData : originDatas)
1690 CacheStorage::Engine::clearCachesForOrigin(*this, sessionID, SecurityOriginData { originData }, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1691 }
1692
1693 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::SessionStorage) && m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
1694 m_storageManagerSet->deleteSessionStorageForOrigins(sessionID, originDatas, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1695
1696 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage) && m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
1697 m_storageManagerSet->deleteLocalStorageForOrigins(sessionID, originDatas, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1698
1699 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases) && !sessionID.isEphemeral())
1700 webIDBServer(sessionID).closeAndDeleteDatabasesForOrigins(originDatas, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1701
1702#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
1703 bool clearServiceWorkers = websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache) || websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations);
1704 if (clearServiceWorkers && !sessionID.isEphemeral()) {
1705 auto& server = swServerForSession(sessionID);
1706 for (auto& originData : originDatas)
1707 server.clear(originData, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1708 }
1709#endif
1710
1711 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache) && !sessionID.isEphemeral()) {
1712 forEachNetworkSession([originDatas, &clearTasksHandler](auto& session) {
1713 clearDiskCacheEntries(session.cache(), originDatas, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1714 });
1715 }
1716
1717 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Credentials)) {
1718 if (auto* session = storageSession(sessionID)) {
1719 for (auto& originData : originDatas)
1720 session->credentialStorage().removeCredentialsWithOrigin(originData);
1721 }
1722 WebCore::CredentialStorage::removeSessionCredentialsWithOrigins(originDatas);
1723 }
1724
1725#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1726 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ResourceLoadStatistics)) {
1727 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1728 for (auto& domain : registrableDomains) {
1729 if (auto* resourceLoadStatistics = networkSession->resourceLoadStatistics())
1730 resourceLoadStatistics->removeDataForDomain(domain, [clearTasksHandler] { });
1731 }
1732 }
1733 }
1734#endif
1735
1736 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1737 HashSet<WebCore::RegistrableDomain> domainsToDeleteNetworkDataFor;
1738 for (auto& originData : originDatas)
1739 domainsToDeleteNetworkDataFor.add(WebCore::RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(originData.host));
1740 for (auto& cookieHostName : cookieHostNames)
1741 domainsToDeleteNetworkDataFor.add(WebCore::RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(cookieHostName));
1742 for (auto& cacheHostName : HSTSCacheHostNames)
1743 domainsToDeleteNetworkDataFor.add(WebCore::RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(cacheHostName));
1744 for (auto& domain : registrableDomains)
1745 domainsToDeleteNetworkDataFor.add(domain);
1746
1747 networkSession->removeNetworkWebsiteData(std::nullopt, WTFMove(domainsToDeleteNetworkDataFor), [clearTasksHandler] { });
1748 }
1749}
1750
1751#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1752static Vector<String> filterForRegistrableDomains(const Vector<RegistrableDomain>& registrableDomains, const HashSet<String>& foundValues)
1753{
1754 Vector<String> result;
1755 for (const auto& value : foundValues) {
1756 if (registrableDomains.contains(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(value)))
1757 result.append(value);
1758 }
1759
1760 return result;
1761}
1762
1763static Vector<WebsiteData::Entry> filterForRegistrableDomains(const Vector<RegistrableDomain>& registrableDomains, const Vector<WebsiteData::Entry>& foundValues)
1764{
1765 Vector<WebsiteData::Entry> result;
1766 for (const auto& value : foundValues) {
1767 if (registrableDomains.contains(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(value.origin.host)))
1768 result.append(value);
1769 }
1770
1771 return result;
1772}
1773
1774static Vector<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> filterForRegistrableDomains(const HashSet<WebCore::SecurityOriginData>& origins, const Vector<RegistrableDomain>& domainsToDelete, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domainsDeleted)
1775{
1776 Vector<SecurityOriginData> originsDeleted;
1777 for (const auto& origin : origins) {
1778 auto domain = RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(origin.host);
1779 if (!domainsToDelete.contains(domain))
1780 continue;
1781 originsDeleted.append(origin);
1782 domainsDeleted.add(domain);
1783 }
1784
1785 return originsDeleted;
1786}
1787
1788void NetworkProcess::deleteAndRestrictWebsiteDataForRegistrableDomains(PAL::SessionID sessionID, OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> websiteDataTypes, RegistrableDomainsToDeleteOrRestrictWebsiteDataFor&& domains, bool shouldNotifyPage, CompletionHandler<void(const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&)>&& completionHandler)
1789{
1790 OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions = WebsiteDataFetchOption::DoNotCreateProcesses;
1791
1792 struct CallbackAggregator final : public ThreadSafeRefCounted<CallbackAggregator> {
1793 explicit CallbackAggregator(CompletionHandler<void(const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&)>&& completionHandler)
1794 : m_completionHandler(WTFMove(completionHandler))
1795 {
1796 }
1797
1798 ~CallbackAggregator()
1799 {
1800 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(m_completionHandler), domains = WTFMove(m_domains)] () mutable {
1801 completionHandler(domains);
1802 });
1803 }
1804
1805 CompletionHandler<void(const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&)> m_completionHandler;
1806 HashSet<RegistrableDomain> m_domains;
1807 };
1808
1809 auto callbackAggregator = adoptRef(*new CallbackAggregator([this, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), shouldNotifyPage] (const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domainsWithData) mutable {
1810 if (shouldNotifyPage)
1811 parentProcessConnection()->send(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::NotifyWebsiteDataDeletionForRegistrableDomainsFinished(), 0);
1812
1813 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), domainsWithData = crossThreadCopy(domainsWithData)] () mutable {
1814 completionHandler(domainsWithData);
1815 });
1816 }));
1817
1818 HashSet<String> hostNamesWithCookies;
1819 HashSet<String> hostNamesWithHSTSCache;
1820 Vector<String> hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete;
1821 auto domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor = domains.domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor;
1822 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies)) {
1823 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID)) {
1824 networkStorageSession->getHostnamesWithCookies(hostNamesWithCookies);
1825
1826 hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(domains.domainsToDeleteAllCookiesFor, hostNamesWithCookies);
1827 networkStorageSession->deleteCookiesForHostnames(hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete, WebCore::IncludeHttpOnlyCookies::Yes);
1828
1829 for (const auto& host : hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete)
1830 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(host));
1831
1832 hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(domains.domainsToDeleteAllButHttpOnlyCookiesFor, hostNamesWithCookies);
1833 networkStorageSession->deleteCookiesForHostnames(hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete, WebCore::IncludeHttpOnlyCookies::No);
1834
1835 for (const auto& host : hostnamesWithCookiesToDelete)
1836 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(host));
1837 }
1838 }
1839
1840 Vector<String> hostnamesWithHSTSToDelete;
1841#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || USE(SOUP)
1842 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::HSTSCache)) {
1843 hostNamesWithHSTSCache = this->hostNamesWithHSTSCache(sessionID);
1844 hostnamesWithHSTSToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, hostNamesWithHSTSCache);
1845
1846 for (const auto& host : hostnamesWithHSTSToDelete)
1847 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(host));
1848
1849 deleteHSTSCacheForHostNames(sessionID, hostnamesWithHSTSToDelete);
1850 }
1851#endif
1852
1853#if HAVE(CFNETWORK_ALTERNATIVE_SERVICE)
1854 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::AlternativeServices)) {
1855 if (auto* networkSession = this->networkSession(sessionID)) {
1856 Vector<String> registrableDomainsToDelete;
1857 registrableDomainsToDelete.reserveInitialCapacity(domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.size());
1858 for (auto& domain : domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor)
1859 registrableDomainsToDelete.uncheckedAppend(domain.string());
1860 networkSession->deleteAlternativeServicesForHostNames(registrableDomainsToDelete);
1861 }
1862 }
1863#endif
1864
1865 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Credentials)) {
1866 if (auto* session = storageSession(sessionID)) {
1867 auto origins = session->credentialStorage().originsWithCredentials();
1868 auto originsToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(origins, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator->m_domains);
1869 for (auto& origin : originsToDelete)
1870 session->credentialStorage().removeCredentialsWithOrigin(origin);
1871 }
1872
1873 auto origins = WebCore::CredentialStorage::originsWithSessionCredentials();
1874 auto originsToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(origins, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator->m_domains);
1875 WebCore::CredentialStorage::removeSessionCredentialsWithOrigins(originsToDelete);
1876 }
1877
1878 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache)) {
1879 CacheStorage::Engine::fetchEntries(*this, sessionID, fetchOptions.contains(WebsiteDataFetchOption::ComputeSizes), [this, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, sessionID, callbackAggregator](auto entries) mutable {
1880
1881 auto entriesToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, entries);
1882
1883 for (const auto& entry : entriesToDelete)
1884 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(entry.origin.host));
1885
1886 for (auto& entry : entriesToDelete)
1887 CacheStorage::Engine::clearCachesForOrigin(*this, sessionID, SecurityOriginData { entry.origin }, [callbackAggregator] { });
1888 });
1889 }
1890
1891 if (m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID)) {
1892 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::SessionStorage)) {
1893 m_storageManagerSet->getSessionStorageOrigins(sessionID, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), this, sessionID, callbackAggregator, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor](auto&& origins) {
1894 if (!m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
1895 return;
1896
1897 auto originsToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(origins, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator->m_domains);
1898 m_storageManagerSet->deleteSessionStorageForOrigins(sessionID, originsToDelete, [callbackAggregator] { });
1899 });
1900 }
1901
1902 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage)) {
1903 m_storageManagerSet->getLocalStorageOrigins(sessionID, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), this, sessionID, callbackAggregator, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor](auto&& origins) {
1904 if (!m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
1905 return;
1906
1907 auto originsToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(origins, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator->m_domains);
1908 m_storageManagerSet->deleteLocalStorageForOrigins(sessionID, originsToDelete, [callbackAggregator] { });
1909 });
1910 }
1911 }
1912
1913 auto path = m_idbDatabasePaths.get(sessionID);
1914 if (!path.isEmpty() && websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases)) {
1915 webIDBServer(sessionID).getOrigins([this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), sessionID, callbackAggregator, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor](auto&& origins) {
1916 if (!m_webIDBServers.contains(sessionID))
1917 return;
1918
1919 auto originsToDelete = filterForRegistrableDomains(origins, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator->m_domains);
1920 webIDBServer(sessionID).closeAndDeleteDatabasesForOrigins(originsToDelete, [callbackAggregator] { });
1921 });
1922 }
1923
1924#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
1925 path = m_serviceWorkerInfo.get(sessionID).databasePath;
1926 bool clearServiceWorkers = websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache) || websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations);
1927 if (clearServiceWorkers && !path.isEmpty()) {
1928 swServerForSession(sessionID).getOriginsWithRegistrations([this, sessionID, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator](const HashSet<SecurityOriginData>& securityOrigins) mutable {
1929 for (auto& securityOrigin : securityOrigins) {
1930 if (!domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.contains(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(securityOrigin.host)))
1931 continue;
1932 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(securityOrigin.host));
1933 swServerForSession(sessionID).clear(securityOrigin, [callbackAggregator] { });
1934 }
1935 });
1936 }
1937#endif
1938
1939 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache)) {
1940 forEachNetworkSession([sessionID, fetchOptions, &domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, &callbackAggregator](auto& session) {
1941 fetchDiskCacheEntries(session.cache(), sessionID, fetchOptions, [domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor, callbackAggregator, session = makeWeakPtr(&session)](auto entries) mutable {
1942 if (!session)
1943 return;
1944
1945 Vector<SecurityOriginData> entriesToDelete;
1946 for (auto& entry : entries) {
1947 if (!domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.contains(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(entry.origin.host)))
1948 continue;
1949 entriesToDelete.append(entry.origin);
1950 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(entry.origin.host));
1951 }
1952 clearDiskCacheEntries(session->cache(), entriesToDelete, [callbackAggregator] { });
1953 });
1954 });
1955 }
1956
1957 auto dataTypesForUIProcess = WebsiteData::filter(websiteDataTypes, WebsiteDataProcessType::UI);
1958 if (!dataTypesForUIProcess.isEmpty() && !domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.isEmpty()) {
1959 CompletionHandler<void(const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&)> completionHandler = [callbackAggregator] (const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domains) {
1960 for (auto& domain : domains)
1961 callbackAggregator->m_domains.add(domain);
1962 };
1963 parentProcessConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::DeleteWebsiteDataInUIProcessForRegistrableDomains(sessionID, dataTypesForUIProcess, fetchOptions, domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor), WTFMove(completionHandler));
1964 }
1965}

1967void NetworkProcess::deleteCookiesForTesting(PAL::SessionID sessionID, RegistrableDomain domain, bool includeHttpOnlyCookies, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1968{
1969 OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> cookieType = WebsiteDataType::Cookies;
1970 RegistrableDomainsToDeleteOrRestrictWebsiteDataFor toDeleteFor;
1971 if (includeHttpOnlyCookies)
1972 toDeleteFor.domainsToDeleteAllCookiesFor.append(domain);
1973 else
1974 toDeleteFor.domainsToDeleteAllButHttpOnlyCookiesFor.append(domain);
1975
1976 deleteAndRestrictWebsiteDataForRegistrableDomains(sessionID, cookieType, WTFMove(toDeleteFor), true, [completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domainsDeletedFor) mutable {
1977 UNUSED_PARAM(domainsDeletedFor);
1978 completionHandler();
1979 });
1980}
1981
1982void NetworkProcess::registrableDomainsWithWebsiteData(PAL::SessionID sessionID, OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> websiteDataTypes, bool shouldNotifyPage, CompletionHandler<void(HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&&)>&& completionHandler)
1983{
1984 OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions = WebsiteDataFetchOption::DoNotCreateProcesses;
1985
1986 struct CallbackAggregator final : public ThreadSafeRefCounted<CallbackAggregator> {
1987 explicit CallbackAggregator(CompletionHandler<void(HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&&)>&& completionHandler)
1988 : m_completionHandler(WTFMove(completionHandler))
1989 {
1990 }
1991
1992 ~CallbackAggregator()
1993 {
1994 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(m_completionHandler), websiteData = WTFMove(m_websiteData)] () mutable {
1995 HashSet<RegistrableDomain> domains;
1996 for (const auto& hostnameWithCookies : websiteData.hostNamesWithCookies)
1997 domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(hostnameWithCookies));
1998
1999 for (const auto& hostnameWithHSTS : websiteData.hostNamesWithHSTSCache)
2000 domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(hostnameWithHSTS));
2001
2002 for (const auto& entry : websiteData.entries)
2003 domains.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(entry.origin.host));
2004
2005 completionHandler(WTFMove(domains));
2006 });
2007 }
2008
2009 CompletionHandler<void(HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&&)> m_completionHandler;
2010 WebsiteData m_websiteData;
2011 };
2012
2013 auto callbackAggregator = adoptRef(*new CallbackAggregator([this, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), shouldNotifyPage] (HashSet<RegistrableDomain>&& domainsWithData) mutable {
2014 if (shouldNotifyPage)
2015 parentProcessConnection()->send(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::NotifyWebsiteDataScanForRegistrableDomainsFinished(), 0);
2016
2017 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), domainsWithData = crossThreadCopy(domainsWithData)] () mutable {
2018 completionHandler(WTFMove(domainsWithData));
2019 });
2020 }));
2021
2022 auto& websiteData = callbackAggregator->m_websiteData;
2023
2024 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies)) {
2025 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID))
2026 networkStorageSession->getHostnamesWithCookies(websiteData.hostNamesWithCookies);
2027 }
2028
2029#if PLATFORM(COCOA) || USE(SOUP)
2030 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::HSTSCache))
2031 websiteData.hostNamesWithHSTSCache = hostNamesWithHSTSCache(sessionID);
2032#endif
2033
2034 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Credentials)) {
2035 if (auto* networkStorageSession = storageSession(sessionID)) {
2036 auto securityOrigins = networkStorageSession->credentialStorage().originsWithCredentials();
2037 for (auto& securityOrigin : securityOrigins)
2038 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ securityOrigin, WebsiteDataType::Credentials, 0 });
2039 }
2040 }
2041
2042 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DOMCache)) {
2043 CacheStorage::Engine::fetchEntries(*this, sessionID, fetchOptions.contains(WebsiteDataFetchOption::ComputeSizes), [callbackAggregator](auto entries) mutable {
2044 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.appendVector(entries);
2045 });
2046 }
2047
2048 auto path = m_idbDatabasePaths.get(sessionID);
2049 if (!path.isEmpty() && websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases)) {
2050 webIDBServer(sessionID).getOrigins([callbackAggregator](auto&& origins) {
2051 while (!origins.isEmpty())
2052 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ origins.takeAny(), WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases, 0 });
2053 });
2054 }
2055
2056#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
2057 path = m_serviceWorkerInfo.get(sessionID).databasePath;
2058 if (!path.isEmpty() && websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations)) {
2059 swServerForSession(sessionID).getOriginsWithRegistrations([callbackAggregator](const HashSet<SecurityOriginData>& securityOrigins) mutable {
2060 for (auto& securityOrigin : securityOrigins)
2061 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.append({ securityOrigin, WebsiteDataType::ServiceWorkerRegistrations, 0 });
2062 });
2063 }
2064#endif
2065
2066 if (websiteDataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache)) {
2067 forEachNetworkSession([sessionID, fetchOptions, &callbackAggregator](auto& session) {
2068 fetchDiskCacheEntries(session.cache(), sessionID, fetchOptions, [callbackAggregator](auto entries) mutable {
2069 callbackAggregator->m_websiteData.entries.appendVector(entries);
2070 });
2071 });
2072 }
2073}
2074#endif // ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)

2118void NetworkProcess::findPendingDownloadLocation(NetworkDataTask& networkDataTask, ResponseCompletionHandler&& completionHandler, const ResourceResponse& response)
2119{
2120 uint64_t destinationID = networkDataTask.pendingDownloadID().toUInt64();
2121
2122 String suggestedFilename = networkDataTask.suggestedFilename();
2123
2124 downloadProxyConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::DownloadProxy::DecideDestinationWithSuggestedFilename(response, suggestedFilename), [this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), networkDataTask = makeRef(networkDataTask)] (String&& destination, SandboxExtension::Handle&& sandboxExtensionHandle, AllowOverwrite allowOverwrite) mutable {
2125 auto downloadID = networkDataTask->pendingDownloadID();
2126 if (destination.isEmpty())
2127 return completionHandler(PolicyAction::Ignore);
2128 networkDataTask->setPendingDownloadLocation(destination, WTFMove(sandboxExtensionHandle), allowOverwrite == AllowOverwrite::Yes);
2129 completionHandler(PolicyAction::Download);
2130 if (networkDataTask->state() == NetworkDataTask::State::Canceling || networkDataTask->state() == NetworkDataTask::State::Completed)
2131 return;
2132
2133 if (downloadManager().download(downloadID)) {
2134 // The completion handler already called dataTaskBecameDownloadTask().
2135 return;
2136 }
2137
2138 downloadManager().downloadDestinationDecided(downloadID, WTFMove(networkDataTask));
2139 }, destinationID);
2140}

2213void NetworkProcess::prepareToSuspend(bool isSuspensionImminent, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
2214{
2215 RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSuspension, "%p - NetworkProcess::prepareToSuspend(), isSuspensionImminent=%d", this, isSuspensionImminent);
2216
2217#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
2218 for (auto& server : m_webIDBServers.values())
2219 server->suspend();
2220#endif
2221
2222 lowMemoryHandler(Critical::Yes);
2223
2224 RefPtr<CallbackAggregator> callbackAggregator = CallbackAggregator::create([this, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
2225 RELEASE_LOG(ProcessSuspension, "%p - NetworkProcess::prepareToSuspend() Process is ready to suspend", this);
2226 UNUSED_VARIABLE(this);
2227 completionHandler();
2228 });
2229
2230#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
2231 WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::suspend([callbackAggregator] { });
2232#endif
2233
2234 forEachNetworkSession([&] (auto& networkSession) {
2235 platformFlushCookies(networkSession.sessionID(), [callbackAggregator] { });
2236 });
2237
2238 for (auto& connection : m_webProcessConnections.values())
2239 connection->cleanupForSuspension([callbackAggregator] { });
2240
2241#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
2242 for (auto& server : m_swServers.values()) {
2243 ASSERT(m_swServers.get(server->sessionID()) == server.get());
2244 server->startSuspension([callbackAggregator] { });
2245 }
2246#endif
2247
2248 m_storageManagerSet->suspend([callbackAggregator] { });
2249}

2267void NetworkProcess::resume()

2271
2272#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
2273 WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::resume();
2274#endif
2275
2276#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
2277 for (auto& server : m_swServers.values())
2278 server->endSuspension();
2279#endif
2280#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
2281 for (auto& server : m_webIDBServers.values())

2283#endif
2284
2285 m_storageManagerSet->resume();

2381void NetworkProcess::resetQuota(PAL::SessionID sessionID, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
2382{
2383 Locker locker { m_sessionStorageQuotaManagersLock };
2384 if (auto* sessionStorageQuotaManager = m_sessionStorageQuotaManagers.get(sessionID)) {
2385 for (auto storageQuotaManager : sessionStorageQuotaManager->existingStorageQuotaManagers())
2386 storageQuotaManager->resetQuotaForTesting();
2387 }
2388 completionHandler();
2389}

2391void NetworkProcess::renameOriginInWebsiteData(PAL::SessionID sessionID, const URL& oldName, const URL& newName, OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
2392{
2393 auto aggregator = CallbackAggregator::create(WTFMove(completionHandler));
2394 auto oldOrigin = WebCore::SecurityOriginData::fromURL(oldName);
2395 auto newOrigin = WebCore::SecurityOriginData::fromURL(newName);
2396
2397 if (oldOrigin.isEmpty() || newOrigin.isEmpty())
2398 return;
2399
2400 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::LocalStorage)) {
2401 if (m_storageManagerSet->contains(sessionID))
2402 m_storageManagerSet->renameOrigin(sessionID, oldName, newName, [aggregator] { });
2403 }
2404
2405 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::IndexedDBDatabases)) {
2406 auto path = m_idbDatabasePaths.get(sessionID);
2407 if (!path.isEmpty())
2408 webIDBServer(sessionID).renameOrigin(oldOrigin, newOrigin, [aggregator] { });
2409 }
2410}

2419SWServer& NetworkProcess::swServerForSession(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
2420{
2421 auto result = m_swServers.ensure(sessionID, [&] {
2422 auto info = m_serviceWorkerInfo.get(sessionID);
2423 auto path = info.databasePath;
2424 // There should already be a registered path for this PAL::SessionID.
2425 // If there's not, then where did this PAL::SessionID come from?
2426 ASSERT(sessionID.isEphemeral() || !path.isEmpty());
2427
2428#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
2429 auto appBoundDomainsCallback = [this, sessionID](auto&& completionHandler) {
2430 parentProcessConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::GetAppBoundDomains { sessionID }, WTFMove(completionHandler), 0);
2431 };
2432#else
2433 auto appBoundDomainsCallback = [] (auto&& completionHandler) {
2434 completionHandler({ });
2435 };
2436#endif
2437 return makeUnique<SWServer>(makeUniqueRef<WebSWOriginStore>(), info.processTerminationDelayEnabled, WTFMove(path), sessionID, parentProcessHasServiceWorkerEntitlement(), [this, sessionID](auto&& jobData, bool shouldRefreshCache, auto&& request, auto&& completionHandler) mutable {
2438 ServiceWorkerSoftUpdateLoader::start(networkSession(sessionID), WTFMove(jobData), shouldRefreshCache, WTFMove(request), WTFMove(completionHandler));
2439 }, [this, sessionID](auto& registrableDomain, auto&& completionHandler) {
2440 ASSERT(!registrableDomain.isEmpty());
2441 parentProcessConnection()->sendWithAsyncReply(Messages::NetworkProcessProxy::EstablishWorkerContextConnectionToNetworkProcess { registrableDomain, sessionID }, WTFMove(completionHandler), 0);
2442 }, WTFMove(appBoundDomainsCallback));
2443 });
2444 return *result.iterator->value;
2445}

2452 return &static_cast<WebSWOriginStore&>(swServer->originStore());

2481void NetworkProcess::requestStorageSpace(PAL::SessionID sessionID, const ClientOrigin& origin, uint64_t quota, uint64_t currentSize, uint64_t spaceRequired, CompletionHandler<void(std::optional<uint64_t>)>&& callback)

2485
2486RefPtr<StorageQuotaManager> NetworkProcess::storageQuotaManager(PAL::SessionID sessionID, const ClientOrigin& origin)
2487{
2488 Locker locker { m_sessionStorageQuotaManagersLock };
2489 auto* sessionStorageQuotaManager = m_sessionStorageQuotaManagers.get(sessionID);
2490 if (!sessionStorageQuotaManager)
2491 return nullptr;
2492
2493 String idbRootPath = sessionStorageQuotaManager->idbRootPath();
2494 StorageQuotaManager::UsageGetter usageGetter = [cacheRootPath = sessionStorageQuotaManager->cacheRootPath().isolatedCopy(), idbRootPath = idbRootPath.isolatedCopy(), origin = origin.isolatedCopy()]() {
2495 ASSERT(!isMainRunLoop());
2496
2497 return CacheStorage::Engine::diskUsage(cacheRootPath, origin) + IDBServer::IDBServer::diskUsage(idbRootPath, origin);
2498 };
2499 StorageQuotaManager::QuotaIncreaseRequester quotaIncreaseRequester = [this, weakThis = makeWeakPtr(*this), sessionID, origin] (uint64_t currentQuota, uint64_t currentSpace, uint64_t requestedIncrease, auto&& callback) {
2500 ASSERT(isMainRunLoop());
2501 if (!weakThis)
2502 callback({ });
2503 requestStorageSpace(sessionID, origin, currentQuota, currentSpace, requestedIncrease, WTFMove(callback));
2504 };
2505
2506 auto originStorageQuotaManager = sessionStorageQuotaManager->ensureOriginStorageQuotaManager(origin, sessionStorageQuotaManager->defaultQuota(origin), WTFMove(usageGetter), WTFMove(quotaIncreaseRequester)).ptr();
2507 return originStorageQuotaManager;
2508}

2736bool NetworkProcess::shouldDisableCORSForRequestTo(PageIdentifier pageIdentifier, const URL& url) const
2737{
2738 return WTF::anyOf(m_extensionCORSDisablingPatterns.get(pageIdentifier), [&] (const auto& pattern) {
2739 return pattern.matches(url);
2740 });
2741}
2742
2743void NetworkProcess::setCORSDisablingPatterns(PageIdentifier pageIdentifier, Vector<String>&& patterns)
2744{
2745 Vector<UserContentURLPattern> parsedPatterns;
2746 parsedPatterns.reserveInitialCapacity(patterns.size());
2747 for (auto&& pattern : WTFMove(patterns)) {
2748 UserContentURLPattern parsedPattern(WTFMove(pattern));
2749 if (parsedPattern.isValid())
2750 parsedPatterns.uncheckedAppend(WTFMove(parsedPattern));
2751 }
2752 parsedPatterns.shrinkToFit();
2753 if (parsedPatterns.isEmpty()) {
2754 m_extensionCORSDisablingPatterns.remove(pageIdentifier);
2755 return;
2756 }
2757 m_extensionCORSDisablingPatterns.set(pageIdentifier, WTFMove(parsedPatterns));
2758}
